    "description": "X Minecraft Launcher (XMCL) 是一个便于你管理多种整合包、模组、资源包、光影包的现代化启动器。它还支持 Minecraft Forge、 Fabric、Quilt、CurseForge 和 Modrinth。",
    "homepage": "https://xmcl.app/",
    "license": "MIT",
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
